{"tid":273420,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係唔想再對朋友好！！！","createTime":"2017-06-06T14:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T08:51:32.000Z","uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ab979d5a7c6873e7ebbe3376591e75de8b0fa6","tid":273420,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"我一心一意對你好 <br />\n就算中間有啲咩過節都好<br />\n我寧願keep住呢份感情 而去選擇唔在意呢啲過節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你對我黎講好重要<br />\n但你視我既好為理所當然 一次又一次利用我對你既鍾意<br />\n我決定左唔再對你好 你又即刻搵返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道我仲有利用既價值<br />\n<br />\n如果你望到呢個post <br />\n希望你擺返個心出黎識朋友<br />\n不過我係唔會再比你利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132d58f32a8eeaa2cd6049bdff30dbca547bdfdb","tid":273420,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<br />\n冇人會珍惜<br />\n因為始終你唔係佢哋心目中最重要嗰個<br />\n已看透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0049578240c363d9143dd62ae559fca223aa6b9b","tid":273420,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"得自己好似隻狗咁 衝埋去同佢搖尾巴 好折墮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1ddfe5321f3bb81e02d222a808a302e244e362","tid":273420,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁架啦<br />\n冇人會珍惜<br />\n因為始終你唔係佢哋心目中最重要嗰個<br />\n已看透<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎我地同病相憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我個case有啲複雜<br />\n佢根本唔當所有人係重要<br />\n我反而係同佢最好朋友<br />\n但佢都唔珍惜我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273b5a1ba751ae22982c67e0ae4ff8e53d3fc0fa","tid":273420,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c